You are a legal entity / business entity with legality as required by Us and the laws and regulations applicable in the legal jurisdiction. If You register on behalf of a business entity, You also represent that You are authorized to act for and on behalf of such legal entity and to enter into and bind such legal entity/entities to the Terms and Conditions;
