Through the Offline Appointment Booking Feature, Users can arrange appointments with Service Providers registered on the Halodoc Platform. If there are any changes or cancellations to the schedule by the selected Service Provider, the User will receive a confirmation regarding the schedule change through the Halodoc Platform.
Transaction Terms for the Offline Appointment Booking Feature
By using the Offline Appointment Booking Feature, Users understand that they have full rights to choose the Service Provider (hospital/clinic or other healthcare facilities) that suits their needs and preferences.
